<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#333333;">
  Hi <%= name %>,
</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#333333;">
  We received a request to reset your Pricewatcher password. Use the secure link below to choose a new password.
</p>
<p style="margin:24px 0;">
  <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;background-color:#c84b43;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;padding:12px 20px;border-radius:8px;">
    Reset password
  </a>
</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#555555;">
  If the button does not work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
</p>
<p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;word-break:break-all;">
  <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" style="color:#c84b43;"><%= resetUrl %></a>
</p>
